comments: Haliburton (IND) makes contact with Young's (ATL) forearm contesting his jump shot attempt.
Huerter (ATL) places his forearm to Smith's (IND) side defending his drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs.
Huerter (ATL) moves along Haliburton's (IND) path and makes marginal contact to his lower body as he releases his pass attempt.
Bogdanovic (ATL) places his hand to Hield's (IND) side defending over the pick and marginal contact occurs.
Smith (IND) hands off the ball in Bogdanovic's (ATL) path and makes marginal contact as he releases away.
Smith (IND) is deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Capela (ATL) delivers contact to Hield's (IND) body after the release defending his driving shot attempt.
Young (ATL) briefly engages with Haliburton (IND) prior to the screen and slightly extends as he releases away from the contact.
Haliburton (IND) briefly places his hands to Young's (ATL) front at the start of his drive and immediately removes them.
Haliburton (IND) places a resting forearm to Young's (ATL) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Hunter (ATL) initiates contact to Washington Jr.'s (IND) body during rebounding and the contact affects his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Huerter (ATL) extends his off-arm into Washington Jr.'s (IND) body and dislodges him from his defensive position.
Huerter (ATL) briefly places two hands against Haliburton's (IND) body and slides his hands off defending his drive.
Bogdanovic (ATL) briefly places his hands against Hield's (IND) body off ball and immediately removes them.
Smith (IND) and Hunter (ATL) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.

Replay review of the foul called on Brissett (IND) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Brissett (IND) initiates contact to Young's (ATL) upper body when he is in his legally obtained rebounding position and the contact affects his ability to get to the loose ball.
Huerter (ATL) and Halliburton (IND) engage and disengage with one another prior to inbound pass.
Smith (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in Bogdanovic's (ATL) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Huerter (ATL) reaches in and makes contact with the ball during Hield's (IND) dribble and he legally resumes his dribble.
Bogdanovic (ATL) places his hand to Hield's (IND) side defending his driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs.
Huerter (ATL) moves laterally in Haliburtons's (IND) path as he sets the screen and makes marginal contact contact as they disengage.
Hield (IND) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Hunter (ATL) moves laterally in Halburton's (IND) space and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Young (ATL) slides his hand against Hield's (IND) body in transition and the marginal contact does not affects his SQBR.
Brissett (IND) makes a marginal brush to Hunter's (ATL) arm as he gathers the loose ball.
